_From @DaveyEdwards on October 1, 2017 18:38_

Possible duplicate of 
https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/google-cloud-node/issues/1820 
and it was moved to 
https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/8860

Although I was not able to get it working with any of the solutions in the thread

There are a couple of issues here: the first load error is likely caused by running `npm install` on Windows then trying to use the result in a Linux docker image. Running `npm rebuild` in the docker container or Dockerfile should fix that.

I don't think the second error is actually caused by gRPC. You can see identical errors reported in [this yarn issue](https://github.com/yarnpkg/yarn/issues/992) with different packages involved.

I had tried the rebuild yesterday without success and tried again after restarting my comp and updating docker today and it is producing the same errors

There is also a warning during install:

```
The case-insensitive file /usr/src/app/node_modules/grpc/node_modules shouldn't be copied twice in one bulk copy
```
What was the output from running `npm rebuild`?
